    "This decision is mostly motivated by how straightforwardly accurate data may be gathered in the Metaverse.",
    "Since fluidity measurements are frequently carried out using information about goods transportation, acquiring a lot of trustworthy data using blockchain technology is very promising as a way to improve goods transportation and boost trip time reliability.",
    "With the decentralized administration and control offered by blockchain, users, and applications can access and exchange IoT data, enhancing user trust and preventing conflicts in the Metaverse.",
